{"id":130169,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/12/中国-中国人民银行上调存贷款基准利率/","date":"2010-12-26T20:35:20Z","modified":"2010-12-26T20:35:20Z","title":"中国: 中国人民银行上调存贷款基准利率","content":"<p><div>\n        中国人民银行上调存贷款基准利率      </div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"\" height=\"257\" src=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_43_large/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/2010-12-07T083235Z_1538668992_GM1E6C71A1H01_RTRMADP_3_CHINA-ECONOMY-RATES_0.JPG\" title=\"\" width=\"344\" /></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>Reuters/Stringer</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n            作者 <a href=\"http://www.chinese.rfi.fr/auteur/%E6%B3%95%E5%B9%BF\" rel=\"nofollow\">法广</a>          </div>\n<p>临近岁末，中国人民银行昨天忽然宣布从今天起上调存贷款基准利率0.25个百分点，这是中国过去3个月内第2次升息。人行在一份简短的声明中指出，将一年期贷款和存款利率各上调25个基点，分别达5.81%和2.75%。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>这是中国当局</p>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}